WEBVTT

00:15:31.464 --> 00:15:34.477
That was an extraordinary moment,

00:15:34.501 --> 00:15:35.667
because ...

00:15:36.278 --> 00:15:38.278
obviously fear is contagious.

00:15:38.909 --> 00:15:40.339
But faith is, too.

00:15:40.363 --> 00:15:43.002
Faith isn't rational or emotional.

00:15:43.811 --> 00:15:44.993
Faith

00:15:46.040 --> 00:15:48.656
is an exercise of the will.

00:15:49.267 --> 00:15:51.901
It's the discipline of the will.

00:15:52.353 --> 00:15:55.824
It's what allows us to transform
everything that we are --

00:15:55.848 --> 00:15:58.146
our weaknesses, our frailties,

00:15:58.170 --> 00:15:59.760
into strength, into power.

00:15:59.784 --> 00:16:01.784
It's truly a transformation.